Methods

Offset-Based
Use parameters like offset and limit to ctrl data retrival
ex. offset=0&limit=100, next call with offset=100
Requires tracking of offsets and can lead to data loss if new data is added during retrieval

Hypermedia
Returns a 'nest' url in the API response,a llowing for straightforward navigation thru pages

Page- Based
Specifying page numbers and requires knowledge of total # of pages

Cursor -Based
Usually combined with hypermedia, uses cursor to keep track of the current position in the dataset and tells you what page to go next

